0 PRODUCTION NOTES:
0   This credits sequence represents the closing of the 72-second
0   opening that began with clouds and title card (Scene 1).
0   It forms a cyclical structure: Sky intro → Family journey → Couch sit → Credits roll
0   The TV display serves as the narrative frame device, showing what
0   the family is watching (and by extension, what the audience is watching).
0 
0 NARRATIVE CLOSURE:
0   The inverse storyboard comes full circle:
0   Scene 1: Sky → text appears (THE SIMPSONS)
0   Scenes 2–9: Family dispersed across Springfield
0   Scene 10: Family converges at home
0   Scene 11 (Credits): TV shows text again (credits / production info)
0   
0   Both bookend scenes feature screen display of text, creating
0   thematic symmetry between opening title and closing credits.
